other_tests.findings: Mild intrahepatic biliary ductal dilation; distended gallbladder containing innumerable stones; thickening and mild adjacent stranding adjacent to the fundus of the gallbladder; small amount of free fluid dependent in the cul-de-sac; new superior endplate compression deformity involving L1.
other_tests.changes_over_time: Mild biliary ductal dilation and gallbladder thickening new from prior CT; previously noted superior endplate compression deformity at L1 is a new finding compared to earlier imaging.
